USE THIS GAME HERE: https://nl.unibet.com/launcher-casino?gamecid=1.7143&realMoney=false

To start use: python roulettebot.py (or any other way of building).
It will ask for positions. You have 3 seconds for each position.
Hover the mouse over the prompted position and wait for the succes.

First hover at the lefttop position of the workspace (hover mouse under the "N" of "COLD NUMBERS")
Second hover at the rightbottom position of the workspace (hover at the rightlower corner of the black even box)

Continue to hover at all prompted points (red, black, spin, clear).

Release mouse and let the cash flow!
